{
  "texts": [
    "The average concreteness score of all the tokens for each complaint constituted our final concreteness score.",
    "We used a t-test to determine whether the concreteness scores for the complaints written by ChatGPT were significantly different from those written by lawyers.",
    "12 The average concreteness score for the ChatGPT-drafted complaints was 2.30 (SD = 0.06).",
    "For lawyer-drafted complaints, the average concreteness was lower, at 2.25 (SD = 0.06).",
    "The concreteness scores for each complaint are reported in \"Appendix 11\"."
  ]
}